WEBVTT

00:52.280 --> 00:53.210
Look, everyone.

00:53.320 --> 00:55.600
This is the archeology excavation site.

00:55.680 --> 00:57.480
They are doing the cleaning now.

01:05.440 --> 01:06.240
What's wrong?

01:06.440 --> 01:07.500
Why the long faces?

01:07.800 --> 01:09.360
There's a disturbance outside the school.

01:09.360 --> 01:11.020
Did it disturb your minds too?

01:11.200 --> 01:14.520
You are too easily distracted by the external environment.

01:14.520 --> 01:15.440
Peace of mind

01:16.200 --> 01:19.360
is a basic quality

01:20.200 --> 01:21.840
for a cultural relics restoration worker.

01:21.840 --> 01:22.440
Sir,

01:22.720 --> 01:24.560
what about the smashed assignments?

01:24.560 --> 01:25.560
Don't worry about that.

01:25.560 --> 01:26.640
Your assignments,

01:26.760 --> 01:29.400
I have already evaluated and graded them.

01:29.440 --> 01:31.100
And I even took photos of them.

01:31.120 --> 01:33.320
Even though Xu Xiao and Yan Xue,

01:33.320 --> 01:34.600
the porcelain for

01:34.800 --> 01:36.240
their two groups' assignments was destroyed,

01:36.240 --> 01:37.300
it doesn't matter.

01:37.320 --> 01:38.479
Your grades are recorded,

01:38.479 --> 01:39.680
and there are photos.

01:39.920 --> 01:41.000
You can freely check them

01:41.000 --> 01:42.600
after class.

01:47.560 --> 01:48.200
Students.

01:48.600 --> 01:49.800
Whether it is history

01:50.560 --> 01:52.280
or a small fragment of life,

01:52.560 --> 01:54.440
it always leaves a trace behind.

01:54.720 --> 01:57.240
No matter how much dirt covers it,

01:57.320 --> 01:58.979
there will eventually be a day

01:59.280 --> 02:00.410
when it shines again

02:00.560 --> 02:02.240
and sees the light of day.

02:03.640 --> 02:04.240
All right,

02:04.640 --> 02:06.100
let's continue our class.

02:07.840 --> 02:08.320
Now,

02:08.560 --> 02:10.199
everyone look at this photo.

02:10.919 --> 02:14.240
These are the characteristics of Ming Chenghua ceramics.

02:23.160 --> 02:24.079
Mr. Yue.

02:25.960 --> 02:27.290
What's wrong, Xiaocen?

02:28.560 --> 02:29.360
If

02:29.960 --> 02:30.760
there are no porcelain fragments

02:30.760 --> 02:33.020
for us to complete the restoration work,

02:33.160 --> 02:34.240
I want to ask

02:34.600 --> 02:36.120
if there's any other way

02:36.120 --> 02:37.780
to prove Xu Xiao's innocence.

02:39.079 --> 02:39.840
At that time,

02:40.160 --> 02:42.000
not a single porcelain fragment from the scene

02:42.000 --> 02:43.320
was left.

02:44.640 --> 02:45.880
I even double-checked.

02:45.880 --> 02:47.480
There wasn't a single piece.

02:49.320 --> 02:51.050
This is really a bit difficult.

02:52.200 --> 02:52.800
By the way.

02:54.000 --> 02:55.840
Are there any photos or something?

02:55.840 --> 02:57.200
They can be used as evidence

02:57.200 --> 02:58.480
for the shape

02:58.560 --> 02:59.890
or patterns of that cup.

03:01.640 --> 03:02.160
Yes.

03:02.800 --> 03:05.200
The antique shop has surveillance cameras.

03:05.200 --> 03:06.260
Thank you, Mr. Yue.

03:06.680 --> 03:07.680
Goodbye, Mr. Yue.

03:09.080 --> 03:09.720
Sir.

03:10.680 --> 03:11.480
Sir.

03:13.120 --> 03:13.680
Sir.

03:16.600 --> 03:17.000
Xiaocen.

03:17.000 --> 03:17.520
Sir,

03:17.800 --> 03:20.730
could you pull up the security footage from that day?

03:23.640 --> 03:25.100
It's about Xu Xiao, right?

03:25.520 --> 03:25.960
Yes.

03:26.840 --> 03:28.500
I heard about the live stream.

03:30.600 --> 03:32.160
I knew you'd come for the footage,

03:32.160 --> 03:33.079
so I got it ready for you.

03:33.079 --> 03:34.010
It's on my phone.

03:34.880 --> 03:36.560
Those people went too far.

03:37.760 --> 03:39.000
They can investigate the bowl if they want,

03:39.000 --> 03:40.640
but why drag Xu Xiao's father into this?

03:40.640 --> 03:42.960
That's an entirely different generation's business.

03:42.960 --> 03:45.480
Sir, you know about Xu Xiao's father?

03:49.600 --> 03:51.480
You are not from around here, so you don't know.

03:51.480 --> 03:53.600
It was a big deal back then.

03:54.000 --> 03:55.160
Xu Xiao

03:55.440 --> 03:57.000
made such a huge mistake.

03:57.440 --> 03:59.370
Why did the school cover up for him?

03:59.760 --> 04:00.560
I looked it up.

04:01.080 --> 04:01.740
It turns out

04:02.120 --> 04:03.880
his teacher, Yue Qixin,

04:04.320 --> 04:05.240
and his father,

04:05.400 --> 04:06.480
Xu Jinsong,

04:06.960 --> 04:07.800
the two of them

04:08.360 --> 04:10.480
were apprentices of the same master.

04:11.080 --> 04:13.680
Xu Jinsong was caught selling fakes back then.

04:13.720 --> 04:14.840
He couldn't take the shock

04:14.840 --> 04:15.920
and lost his mind.

04:16.519 --> 04:18.320
Later, on that ceramics street,

04:18.560 --> 04:20.320
he'd argue with people every day with some fakes,

04:20.320 --> 04:21.779
insisting they were real.

04:22.120 --> 04:23.800
Don't you think this is karma?

04:26.120 --> 04:27.160
These theories,

04:27.160 --> 04:27.800
you don't have to tell me.

04:27.800 --> 04:28.440
I know them all, alright?

04:28.440 --> 04:29.240
No, Xu.

04:29.240 --> 04:30.080
Still the same saying.

04:30.080 --> 04:31.920
When it comes to judging things at a glance,

04:31.920 --> 04:33.980
I, Xu Jinsong, have never been wrong.

04:42.240 --> 04:43.320
How is this faint?

04:46.000 --> 04:48.240
I think Yue Qixin is just jealous.

04:51.720 --> 04:52.800
I, Xu Jinsong,

04:52.800 --> 04:54.120
have never been wrong.

04:55.960 --> 04:57.220
I heard you sell fakes.

04:57.240 --> 04:58.560
Mine must be fake too.

04:58.560 --> 04:59.000
Give me a refund.

04:59.000 --> 04:59.640
Alright.

04:59.640 --> 05:01.480
I, Xu Jinsong, never sell fakes.

05:01.480 --> 05:02.680
Then how do you prove it's not fake?

05:02.680 --> 05:03.720
What do you mean, prove it?

05:03.720 --> 05:05.520
I'm telling you, I've never sold fakes.

05:05.520 --> 05:06.450
Give me a refund.

05:21.360 --> 05:22.000
Mr. Yue.

05:23.120 --> 05:24.320
The shape is correct.

05:25.280 --> 05:27.680
But the surveillance video is too blurry.

05:27.960 --> 05:29.290
I can't see the pattern.

05:29.480 --> 05:30.200
Mr. Yue,

05:30.760 --> 05:31.880
what should we do?

05:32.880 --> 05:33.480
Mr. Yue.

05:37.560 --> 05:38.840
What is it, Xu Xiao?

05:47.680 --> 05:49.480
I want to take a break from school

05:49.880 --> 05:51.280
and handle this matter properly.

05:51.280 --> 05:52.680
Don't let this matter

05:52.680 --> 05:53.880
delay your progress.

05:54.159 --> 05:55.360
You should still prioritize your studies.

05:55.360 --> 05:55.920
Xu Xiao,

05:56.520 --> 05:57.600
there must be a way.

05:58.400 --> 06:01.120
We have a unified garbage station in Jingdezhen.

06:01.120 --> 06:02.240
If archeology workers

06:02.240 --> 06:05.760
can excavate tens of thousands of porcelain shards from underground,

06:05.760 --> 06:06.560
then I can also find

06:06.560 --> 06:08.600
the fragments of that blue-and-white porcelain bowl.

06:08.600 --> 06:09.480
Xiaocen,

06:10.240 --> 06:12.370
that's not what I meant by persisting.

06:12.880 --> 06:14.410
Do you know how much garbage

06:14.480 --> 06:16.960
a city produces in a single day?

06:18.000 --> 06:18.600
Nonsense.

06:20.520 --> 06:21.760
I will solve it myself.

06:21.760 --> 06:22.240
Xu Xiao,

06:22.680 --> 06:23.640
about this matter,

06:23.640 --> 06:25.700
I suggest you consider it carefully.

06:25.760 --> 06:26.490
Understood?

06:38.440 --> 06:39.000
Xu Xiao.

06:41.120 --> 06:41.800
Xu Xiao.

06:43.440 --> 06:44.000
Xu Xiao.

06:45.960 --> 06:47.960
We are all still trying to find a way.

06:48.800 --> 06:50.800
Making such a decision at this time,

06:51.200 --> 06:51.920
will taking a leave of absence solve it?

06:51.920 --> 06:53.980
I told you I have my own way to solve it.

06:55.280 --> 06:57.940
How could I really let you dig through the trash?

07:22.280 --> 07:22.720
Mom.

07:24.680 --> 07:26.940
About that matter you mentioned before,

07:27.360 --> 07:28.820
I have thought it through.

07:33.600 --> 07:34.320
Today,

07:36.080 --> 07:38.810
I have applied for a leave of absence from school.

07:40.480 --> 07:41.080
Really.

07:43.000 --> 07:44.240
That's great, son.

07:45.760 --> 07:46.960
I'll have your uncle

07:46.960 --> 07:48.890
look for the best tutor right away.

07:49.560 --> 07:51.920
Don't worry. Your grades have always been good.

07:51.920 --> 07:52.640
Anyway,

07:52.680 --> 07:54.640
no matter what major you choose later,

07:54.640 --> 07:56.500
you won't fall behind your peers.

07:58.600 --> 07:59.200
Got it.

08:00.840 --> 08:04.370
The most important thing when choosing a major is to be careful.

08:04.480 --> 08:05.880
Mom will help you choose.

08:07.760 --> 08:09.360
Um, Xu Xiao.

08:11.560 --> 08:13.690
Have you really thought this through?

08:14.600 --> 08:15.960
What are you talking about?

08:15.960 --> 08:18.080
Didn't I tell you to find a tutor?

08:18.320 --> 08:19.520
Right, right, right.

08:19.800 --> 08:21.130
I'll go contact one now.

08:23.320 --> 08:23.920
Son.

08:24.560 --> 08:27.920
I'm really glad that you're willing to listen to mom on this matter.

08:27.920 --> 08:29.360
I really feel happy.

08:33.960 --> 08:36.400
We've talked about cleaning before.

08:36.520 --> 08:38.650
For cleaning, we need rough cleaning,

08:38.840 --> 08:40.799
and use a professional cleaning agent

08:40.799 --> 08:42.520
for precise wiping.

08:42.799 --> 08:43.880
After that,

08:43.960 --> 08:46.600
we will proceed to the next step, rejoining.

08:47.320 --> 08:48.960
For rejoining, please note

08:49.440 --> 08:51.570
that it must be aligned with the notch.

10:02.320 --> 10:03.050
Look at mine.

10:04.560 --> 10:06.960
I heard Xu Xiao is about to change his major.

10:08.120 --> 10:09.680
The school isn't holding him accountable anymore,

10:09.680 --> 10:10.760
so why is he dropping out?

10:10.760 --> 10:11.200
Exactly.

10:11.200 --> 10:12.720
It seems he brought it up himself.

10:12.720 --> 10:13.640
He shouldn't.

10:13.800 --> 10:15.320
Mr. Yue even spoke up for him.

10:15.320 --> 10:16.600
Don't spread fake news.

10:16.600 --> 10:17.040
Right.

10:17.040 --> 10:18.520
When I was walking over from the office just now,

10:18.520 --> 10:19.200
I heard it.

10:20.600 --> 10:22.440
Zhang Jiatian was already making trouble for the school.

10:22.440 --> 10:22.880
Exactly.

10:22.880 --> 10:24.520
Now he has more to complain about.

10:24.520 --> 10:26.280
What's the idiom for that?

10:26.360 --> 10:27.640
Confess without being pressed.

10:27.640 --> 10:29.040
That's not how you use it.

10:29.200 --> 10:29.560
No.

10:29.920 --> 10:32.320
I don't think Xu Xiao will give up so easily.

10:33.360 --> 10:34.440
Okay, class.

10:34.440 --> 10:35.570
The teacher is here.

10:35.920 --> 10:37.240
Everyone, take your seats.

10:37.240 --> 10:38.300
Class is starting.

10:45.200 --> 10:45.840
Use this glue.

10:45.840 --> 10:47.840
You need to apply it like this. Look.

10:49.440 --> 10:52.600
I didn't expect Mr. Yue to put us in the same group.

10:53.600 --> 10:55.040
Let me make this clear first.

10:55.040 --> 10:57.160
Even though I'm good friends with Yuexin,

10:57.160 --> 10:59.240
I support the freedom to love.

10:59.480 --> 11:01.560
So whoever ends up with whom,

11:01.560 --> 11:01.960
No.

11:01.960 --> 11:03.440
I will give my blessing. No...

11:03.440 --> 11:05.960
Also, I'm pretty clumsy,

11:06.280 --> 11:08.920
so don't expect too much from me.

11:09.360 --> 11:09.760
Please

11:10.720 --> 11:11.920
bear with me.

11:20.440 --> 11:20.970
Xiaocen.

11:22.520 --> 11:23.980
Where are you going later?

11:30.840 --> 11:31.840
This is so cute.

11:37.400 --> 11:37.930
Xiaocen.

11:39.280 --> 11:42.410
Isn't that the person who took advantage of us last time?

11:45.040 --> 11:46.500
It is her. It's really her.

11:51.400 --> 11:51.930
She left.

11:52.440 --> 11:54.170
Let's go take advantage of her.

12:05.600 --> 12:07.720
Awesome.

12:10.040 --> 12:11.480
So cute. Look.

12:12.120 --> 12:12.560
For you.

12:12.560 --> 12:13.680
It's so cute.

12:13.720 --> 12:14.920
Thank you, Yuexin.

12:22.160 --> 12:22.800
Xiaocen,

12:23.640 --> 12:26.040
do you know how I noticed Xu Xiao?

12:31.800 --> 12:33.720
Your girls' group failed the military posture.

12:33.720 --> 12:35.240
What's wrong with me punishing her?

12:35.240 --> 12:36.480
Why are you talking back to me?

12:36.480 --> 12:38.280
Wu Jing has already tried her best.

12:38.280 --> 12:39.800
If you keep making her stand like this,

12:39.800 --> 12:41.200
she will get heatstroke.

12:41.240 --> 12:42.570
I don't think I'm wrong.

12:42.880 --> 12:43.440
Fine.

12:43.800 --> 12:45.600
You take the punishment for her.

12:50.120 --> 12:50.980
I'm Lin Yuexin.

12:54.360 --> 12:55.000
Xu Xiao.

12:57.240 --> 12:59.320
When the instructor scolded us just now,

12:59.320 --> 13:00.520
you didn't say a word.

13:01.280 --> 13:02.940
So why are you being punished?

13:03.040 --> 13:04.240
Because in our group,

13:04.280 --> 13:05.920
some boys didn't do their chores well.

13:05.920 --> 13:06.800
Then why

13:07.120 --> 13:08.780
are you the only one punished?

13:09.200 --> 13:09.720
There's also him.

13:09.720 --> 13:10.600
Lap 7.

13:11.120 --> 13:12.240
Eight more laps.

13:13.400 --> 13:14.730
I can't do this anymore.

13:15.920 --> 13:17.600
Why did they choose you as the group leader?

13:17.600 --> 13:18.730
I don't know either.

13:19.440 --> 13:21.560
It seems since the first grade,

13:21.960 --> 13:24.160
I've been the class monitor every year.

13:25.720 --> 13:28.380
Then why did they choose you as the group leader?

13:28.600 --> 13:30.660
Because I'm the tallest in our class.

13:35.280 --> 13:37.040
Probably from that time on,

13:37.680 --> 13:39.800
I became curious about this boy.

13:41.040 --> 13:42.040
His excellence

13:42.360 --> 13:44.560
and a kind of inexplicable persistence

13:45.760 --> 13:47.360
are very attractive, right?

13:48.800 --> 13:50.000
But,

13:50.480 --> 13:51.560
over time,

13:52.040 --> 13:53.320
I felt that this kind of

13:53.560 --> 13:54.320
care

13:54.560 --> 13:55.480
and concern

13:56.800 --> 13:58.360
was more of an admiration.

14:00.560 --> 14:01.680
Actually,

14:03.480 --> 14:05.800
the last time I volunteered to form a team

14:07.240 --> 14:08.440
was because of myself.

14:08.440 --> 14:09.120
Xiaocen,

14:09.560 --> 14:11.800
you don't need to explain anything to me.

14:11.800 --> 14:13.440
Just do what you want to do.

14:17.360 --> 14:18.720
Yuexin, you're so nice.

14:20.440 --> 14:21.000
What,

14:21.040 --> 14:22.500
are you friend-zoning me?

14:22.760 --> 14:23.560
No.

14:23.920 --> 14:25.200
I'm serious.

14:26.360 --> 14:28.160
When I first came to this school,

14:28.400 --> 14:30.330
no one really paid attention to me.

14:30.960 --> 14:32.560
Only you were very warm to me.

14:33.480 --> 14:35.360
Even today, you asked me out

14:35.360 --> 14:36.480
just to comfort me.

14:37.920 --> 14:39.980
I know everything you've done for me.

14:44.120 --> 14:45.450
Xiaocen, you know what?

14:46.320 --> 14:48.850
Actually, I used to transfer schools a lot too

14:48.880 --> 14:50.480
because of my parents' jobs.

14:51.520 --> 14:53.520
Most of the time when I transferred,

14:53.520 --> 14:55.250
everyone was pretty nice to me.

14:56.280 --> 14:57.740
But there was this one time

14:58.440 --> 15:00.370
when I ran into a little situation.

15:00.960 --> 15:01.840
Once,

15:02.200 --> 15:03.860
I was walking down the street.

15:04.160 --> 15:05.760
Suddenly, a boy rushed out,

15:06.160 --> 15:06.800
and told me

15:07.640 --> 15:08.520
he liked me.

15:09.400 --> 15:10.930
Sounds pretty good, right?

15:12.960 --> 15:14.760
But I panicked,

15:14.960 --> 15:16.690
and just ran away immediately.

15:17.680 --> 15:18.720
And then,

15:19.800 --> 15:21.480
a girl who liked him

15:21.600 --> 15:23.260
brought a whole bunch of girls

15:23.360 --> 15:25.090
to my classroom looking for me.

15:25.160 --> 15:26.690
She said she wanted to talk.

15:27.760 --> 15:30.160
Of course, it didn't escalate to bullying.

15:30.480 --> 15:31.400
After that,

15:31.440 --> 15:32.960
during meals at the cafeteria,

15:32.960 --> 15:34.760
they never approached me again.

15:35.160 --> 15:37.200
They would always eat together in a group.

15:37.200 --> 15:38.040
I could only

15:38.840 --> 15:39.920
eat all by myself.

15:43.600 --> 15:45.240
To be honest, those days

15:45.800 --> 15:47.640
were really quite tough.

15:49.640 --> 15:50.520
So at school,

15:50.520 --> 15:51.760
when I saw you alone,

15:52.280 --> 15:54.540
it immediately reminded me of that time.

15:57.760 --> 15:59.040
I really didn't want you

15:59.040 --> 16:01.500
to go through the same unhappy times as I did.

16:03.240 --> 16:04.000
Yuexin.

16:07.240 --> 16:08.040
All right.

16:08.440 --> 16:10.100
Look, I'm perfectly fine now.

16:10.200 --> 16:11.360
You need to pull yourself together.

16:11.360 --> 16:12.690
Xu Xiao needs your help.

16:38.800 --> 16:39.600
Ducktor Sui,

16:40.520 --> 16:41.640
a susancai duck-shaped incense burner

16:41.640 --> 16:44.100
from the Chenghua reign of the Ming Dynasty.

16:44.120 --> 16:45.560
It is 25.3 centimeters tall.

16:45.560 --> 16:46.960
It consists of upper and lower parts.

16:46.960 --> 16:48.200
The upper part is a lid,

16:48.200 --> 16:50.460
and the lower part is for holding spices.

16:52.240 --> 16:52.970
Remember me?

16:55.120 --> 16:57.520
You're that talkative person from last time.

16:57.520 --> 16:58.880
I don't know if that's a good impression

16:58.880 --> 16:59.800
or a bad one.

17:00.680 --> 17:02.480
Why do I always run into you here?

17:02.640 --> 17:03.960
Because you wander around here

17:03.960 --> 17:05.690
every Wednesday and Thursday.

17:08.480 --> 17:09.359
Don't get me wrong.

17:09.359 --> 17:10.480
I'm not a creep.

17:11.119 --> 17:12.560
I just work here.

17:15.160 --> 17:16.819
Since you like it here so much,

17:16.920 --> 17:18.780
do you want to learn more about it?

17:52.640 --> 17:54.520
Jingdezhen Imperial Kiln Museum used to be the Imperial Kiln Factory.

17:54.520 --> 17:55.640
The porcelain fired here

17:55.640 --> 17:56.970
was all for the emperor.

17:57.480 --> 17:59.140
So for those defective pieces

17:59.320 --> 18:00.650
or the unselected ones,

18:00.680 --> 18:02.240
to prevent them from falling into the hands of the common people,

18:02.240 --> 18:04.600
they all had to be smashed and buried underground.

18:04.600 --> 18:06.200
That's why at the Jingdezhen Imperial Kiln Museum,

18:06.200 --> 18:08.860
every piece of porcelain you see is incomplete,

18:09.040 --> 18:11.600
all restored from unearthed fragments.

18:13.280 --> 18:15.000
Every time I come to this exhibition hall

18:15.000 --> 18:16.730
and see these broken exhibits,

18:17.480 --> 18:18.760
I feel a bit sad.

18:19.280 --> 18:19.680
Why?

18:21.120 --> 18:23.380
After countless times of starting over,

18:23.520 --> 18:24.880
finally picking one out of ten thousand,

18:24.880 --> 18:26.920
a perfect piece of porcelain is fired.

18:26.920 --> 18:28.440
But if you simultaneously fire two

18:28.440 --> 18:30.040
perfect pieces of porcelain,

18:30.040 --> 18:31.700
you have to smash the other one

18:32.200 --> 18:32.960
to ensure

18:33.160 --> 18:34.760
the uniqueness

18:34.760 --> 18:36.680
and integrity of the tribute to the emperor.

18:36.680 --> 18:39.280
If I were that other perfect piece of porcelain

18:39.760 --> 18:40.840
but was smashed,

18:42.120 --> 18:43.920
I'd probably hold a deep grudge.

18:44.520 --> 18:45.800
But I've also heard

18:45.920 --> 18:47.400
that they are like the exam papers

18:47.400 --> 18:49.000
you did in your student days.

18:49.000 --> 18:51.320
You only have to hand in one final answer sheet,

18:51.320 --> 18:52.250
but before that,

18:52.400 --> 18:55.330
you have to hand in countless trial and error papers.

18:57.200 --> 18:58.040
I think

18:58.640 --> 19:00.370
both brokenness and wholeness

19:00.600 --> 19:01.730
are a kind of beauty.

19:05.880 --> 19:07.210
Babies in the live room.

19:07.280 --> 19:09.480
The Jingdezhen Ceramic University incident

19:09.480 --> 19:10.280
has an update.

19:10.640 --> 19:11.840
This guy named Xu Xiao

19:11.880 --> 19:13.560
has been expelled by

19:13.880 --> 19:14.920
Ceramic University.

19:14.920 --> 19:16.960
This proves that every word I said

19:16.960 --> 19:17.840
is true.

19:18.000 --> 19:18.460
Second,

19:18.880 --> 19:19.640
this school,

19:20.040 --> 19:22.840
they also feel that they can't keep such a student.

19:23.440 --> 19:26.000
He clearly took a voluntary leave of absence.

19:26.360 --> 19:30.680
How was it twisted into being expelled?

19:32.800 --> 19:33.530
In a few days,

19:33.800 --> 19:35.330
I'm going to hold an offline

19:35.680 --> 19:38.280
small cultural relics appreciation meeting.

19:38.560 --> 19:40.120
What I can offer everyone this time

19:40.120 --> 19:41.480
is the best treasure I've collected

19:41.480 --> 19:42.480
in the past two years.

19:42.480 --> 19:45.160
Don't believe him.

19:46.320 --> 19:48.120
We can trade on the spot.

19:48.280 --> 19:49.280
I got blocked.

19:49.760 --> 19:50.680
All my friends

19:50.680 --> 19:51.680
can participate.

19:55.040 --> 19:56.720
I think Xiaoyi and Wang Lin's relationship

19:56.720 --> 19:57.920
is already on the rocks.

19:57.920 --> 19:59.780
Xiaoyi often says in the dorm that

20:00.360 --> 20:02.320
Wang Lin is a chauvinist

20:02.320 --> 20:03.480
and acts on a whim.

20:03.480 --> 20:05.400
He takes her to basketball

20:05.800 --> 20:06.800
courts every day,

20:07.640 --> 20:09.440
internet cafes, and pool halls.

20:10.040 --> 20:12.170
How could a girl like places like that?

20:12.600 --> 20:13.840
I think they are done.

20:15.680 --> 20:17.480
How far along are we?

20:18.600 --> 20:20.760
We just need to let the epoxy resin adhesive

20:20.760 --> 20:21.800
seep in.

20:22.680 --> 20:23.520
I'm sorry.

20:23.520 --> 20:25.600
Have I been talking the whole time?

20:25.960 --> 20:27.440
I made you do all the work.

20:28.400 --> 20:29.000
It's fine.

20:29.800 --> 20:30.920
You're the best.

20:45.720 --> 20:46.600
Xu Xiao.

20:47.920 --> 20:49.440
How are you really doing?

20:52.280 --> 20:53.960
What can I do for you?

21:10.320 --> 21:11.760
To all the darlings in the livestream room,

21:11.760 --> 21:13.400
Xu Xiao's parent

21:13.560 --> 21:14.560
contacted me again.

21:14.560 --> 21:15.760
He took the initiative to contact me.

21:15.760 --> 21:16.560
And what did he say?

21:16.560 --> 21:18.480
He even wanted to settle with me voluntarily.

21:18.480 --> 21:19.880
My terms are very simple.

21:19.880 --> 21:20.540
Three days.

21:21.440 --> 21:22.840
A three-day deadline.

21:23.440 --> 21:25.400
If you can't pay the 300,000,

21:25.560 --> 21:26.960
I'll see you in court.

21:49.920 --> 21:50.640
Xu Xiao.

21:57.600 --> 21:58.000
Here.

22:01.440 --> 22:04.100
This is our smashed blue-and-white porcelain.

22:05.280 --> 22:06.360
You fixed it.

22:10.240 --> 22:11.900
I've been looking for a chance

22:12.440 --> 22:14.040
to give it to you personally.

22:20.400 --> 22:20.960
Xiaocen.

22:24.520 --> 22:26.920
I might have to transfer to another school.

22:32.200 --> 22:33.280
How can you?

22:35.760 --> 22:36.840
You are so talented,

22:36.840 --> 22:38.570
and you love this major so much.

22:39.800 --> 22:40.680
Some things

22:42.280 --> 22:43.080
happen

22:44.280 --> 22:45.940
even if you don't want them to.

22:51.320 --> 22:52.280
Xu Xiao.

22:56.120 --> 22:56.840
It was because of you

22:56.840 --> 22:58.770
that I fell in love with this major.

23:00.880 --> 23:01.440
No.

23:03.040 --> 23:04.440
I know better than anyone

23:05.320 --> 23:07.780
that you have fallen in love with this major.

23:11.360 --> 23:12.120
I remember the first time

23:12.120 --> 23:14.120
you saw Xiao Qing after it was fired.

23:23.000 --> 23:23.840
No matter

23:25.320 --> 23:27.120
if I'm by your side in the future,

23:28.760 --> 23:29.640
I hope

23:30.920 --> 23:32.380
you can keep going firmly.

23:53.080 --> 23:53.680
Here.

23:57.160 --> 23:59.080
Try my premium Fuliang tea.

23:59.920 --> 24:00.780
Thank you, sir.

24:06.160 --> 24:07.960
I know you guys

24:09.840 --> 24:11.100
are having a hard time.

24:12.720 --> 24:13.440
But

24:14.920 --> 24:15.780
it will be fine.

24:16.600 --> 24:17.460
It will be fine.

24:21.680 --> 24:22.540
Drink your tea.

24:28.360 --> 24:28.960
Mr. Fatty.

24:29.640 --> 24:31.000
You ate the food and drank the water.

24:31.000 --> 24:31.920
Don't disturb my sleep.

24:31.920 --> 24:32.400
Hear me?

24:32.800 --> 24:33.400
Thank you.

24:43.400 --> 24:45.260
Mr. Fatty has princess syndrome.

24:45.800 --> 24:47.880
He's always trying to get my attention.

24:47.880 --> 24:50.120
Every now and then, he takes some

24:50.560 --> 24:51.880
shiny things from my desk.
